  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 05/23/2022 at 11:30pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.18.6-Improvements\">Improvements</h3><ul><li><p>Improved Square transaction handling to reduce \u201cError 500.\u201d</p></li><li><p>Improved Square transaction process to prevent a user error possibility, which ended in duplicate transactions.</p></li><li><p>Improved Square transaction process to prevent &quot;failed transactions&quot; from resolving multiple times with client handling, which ended in multiple unique transactions.</p></li><li><p>The Cash Reconciliation Report now uses proper report dates for its Gateway transactions.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.6-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Fixed an issue where the Reconciliation Report reflects Square transactions inaccurately.</p></li><li><p>Resolved a bug where transactions would sometimes duplicate with the same Transaction ID.</p></li><li><p>Square no longer gets stuck in a confirmation loop, and no longer attempts to charge the customer again when stuck in this loop.</p></li><li><p>Improved the Switch User feature so that the Assigned VCT does not switch with the employee.</p></li><li><p>Updating Billing Terms for customers now saves the updated information properly.</p></li><li><p>The Import Customer Template now works again as intended.</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
